milestones.description: Allan Donald has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (9) for SA, going past Adrian Kuiper
Dave Houghton has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (18) for ZIM, going past Andy Pycroft
Wessels has broken the record for most catches (6) in ODIs for SA, going past McMillan's 4
Wessels and Peter Kirsten's 112-run partnership is SA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 111 between Wessels and Peter Kirsten
Wessels and Peter Kirsten's 112-run partnership is SA's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 111 between Peter Kirsten and Wessels
